'''Narmacil''' may refer to:
* [[Narmacil I]] ({{TA|1049}} - {{TA|1294|n}}), seventeenth [[Kings of Gondor|King of Gondor]] who ruled at the height of [[Gondor]]'s power.
* [[Narmacil II]] ({{TA|1684|}} - {{TA|1856|n}}), twenty-ninth [[Kings of Gondor|King of Gondor]] who was slain in the [[Battle of the Plains]].
